title: Normal Stroma_Patient ID 434
source_name_ch1: LCM-derived cells from snap-frozen tissues of normal stroma
extract_protocol_ch1: Cells were collected from frozen sections using LCM. RNA was isolated with PicoPure RNA isolation KIT (LifeTechnologies). Concentration and Quality of RNA was measured with RNA PicoChip on Bioanalyzer
label_protocol_ch1: RNA was amplified with Ovation Pico WTA System (NuGen) and labeled  with Encor Biotin Module (NuGen)
hyb_protocol: Chips were hybridized to platform GPL570 platform (Affymetrix Human Genome U133 Plus2.0 Array) using Affymetrix HWS KIT and FS450_0004 Protocol
description: Gene expression data of LCM-derived cells from fresh frozen tissues of normal stroma
data_processing: The data were analyzed with Microarray Suite version 5.0 (MAS 5.0) using Affymetrix default analysis.
contact_department: Icahn School of Medicine at Mount Sinai
contact_institute: The Institute for Next Generation Healthcare
